reviews.review: I stopped by here to buy chicken to take home. I eat jollibe a lot but only order the app. This time I stopped by because it was convenient, and the staff was actually very polite and friendly. The service is also dedicated. I have been to many stores and this is one of the places where the staff is very professional and friendly. The quality of the food is that the chicken here is number 1 delicious, crispy and hot. As for the potatoes, they have bad luck, some are crispy and some are cold. The space is a bit small, but there is a dining floor above, the space is clean and has cool air conditioning. The price is moderate, in general quite expensive compared to popular dishes but at such a price the quality is ok and the price is ok and acceptable. I told the employee to get large potatoes for me, but she must have misheard so I got small potatoes. As for the lemon tea, I find it a bit too sweet for my taste
